Rave unstraped and rubbed his head. "Boss? yo boss?" Wing watch for 
help i'm heading over to the sick bay... Rave... MAXIMIZE!" He 
transformed into his streamlined Raven form flying throught the 
wreckage he flew to the ships second half... "Hold on boss."

Wing stroked Sabre's head and hoped someone here had a working 
healing chamber... Sabre's face had been badly damaged and it seemed 
as if he was leaking some fluid...
